    <h1>Primary Sources & References</h1>
    <p class="intro">Every source used on this site, with direct links to the originating official institution. We prioritise official primary sources (statistics offices, treasuries, central banks, international organisations). Where primary data is unavailable, we use peer-reviewed academic work or institutional research, clearly identified as such with the source type, funder, and methodological limits noted.</p>
